               <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__370" type="place">Rostock Universität Patriotischer Weg
                  116a</rs><lb/> 6. " " <rs ref="#tillich_person_id__42" type="person">Althaus</rs>
               <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__136" type="place">Erlangen Universität Hindenburgstr. 4
