                  Kattenbusch</rs>
               <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__189" type="place">Halle a.S. Universität</rs><lb/>
               Fasanenstr. 7<lb/> 8. " " <rs ref="#tillich_person_id__904" type="person">Hirsch</rs>
               <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__186" type="place">Göttingen Bauratgerberstr. 19</rs><lb/>
               9. " "<rs ref="#tillich_person_id__1723" type="person">K. L. Schmidt</rs>
               <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__224" type="place">Jena Karl-Alexanderplatz 5</rs><lb/>
